title: Northlanders Vol. 3 (2008-2009) (Digital) (ZoneKing-Empire)
description:
Northlanders Book 3: Blood in the Snow

Genre - Action/Adventure

English | CBR | 6 Issues

Written by Brian Wood
Art by Dean Ormston, Danijel Zezelj, Davide Gianfelice and Vasilis Lolos

Collects Issues #9,10, 17-20

This volume collects all of the NORTHLANDERS short stories. Exploring everything from the art of Viking single combat, to the role of women in the Viking world
